{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/a013_01_ooglians_steamstore.gif?t=1706622774\" /><br>The tower defense base builder you never realized you wanted!<br>Straight out of a fever dream, here is... Ooglians!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What are Ooglians?</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/a013_03_ooglians_steamstore.gif?t=1706622774\" /><br>Ooglians are a mysterious species.<br>It's unknown whether they are technophobes or destructophiles,<br>but they sure love smashing machinery to bits.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You are not an Ooglian.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/a013_05_ooglians_steamstore.gif?t=1706622774\" /><br>You are... you. It's not up to me to tell you who you are.<br><i>Why</i> are you on this planet?<br><i>What</i> is your goal?<br>It is, as of now, unknown. Maybe if you protect your reactor, you'll find out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO2.gif?t=1706622774\" /> Build the base around your reactor<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO3.gif?t=1706622774\" /> Ooglians are attracted by the machinery<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO4.gif?t=1706622774\" /> Ooglians try to destroy your base<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO5.gif?t=1706622774\" /> Build more machines to defend your base<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO3.gif?t=1706622774\" /> Attract more ooglians<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO6.gif?t=1706622774\" /> It's a game loop<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/smol_WOOOO2.gif?t=1706622774\" /> You lose <span class=\"bb_strike\">when</span> if your reactor dies<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/a013_04_ooglians_steamstore.gif?t=1706622774\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/ooglian_wishlist_now_cropped.gif?t=1706622774\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/OOGLIAN_WOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOH.gif?t=1706622774\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1706622774","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/page.bg.jpg?t=1706622774","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1706622774","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1706622774","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Cartoon Violence"},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><img class=\